*Ponosna* je bila na svoje dete kada je uspešno završilo školovanje. (She was proud of her child when it successfully finished its schooling.)

Njeno ponosno izražavanje bilo je neprikosnoveno. (Her proud expression was unquestioned.)

Njegove *ponosne* reči su ispunile sobu. (His proud words filled the room.)

Mladić je bio veoma *ponosan* na svoju postignuća. (The young man was very proud of his accomplishments.)

Ona je osećala veliku *ponosnu* satisfakciju. (She felt a great sense of pride.)